  "key_strengths": [
    "Four-mode fallback chain handles different execution capabilities gracefully",
    "Explicit prohibition on overstuffed or overclaiming graphical abstracts maintains evidence discipline",
    "Separation of narrative spine identification before visual generation prevents aesthetic-over-evidence prioritization",
    "Clarification-first rule when input is insufficient prevents generation from vague study summaries"
